es to perform discovery. Initially this protocol was designed for https://kubernetes.io[Kubernetes] and https://www.openshift.org[OpenShift] but it suitable for any type of D\nopenssl pom.xml` dependencies:  [source,xml] ---- <dependency>     <groupId>org.wildfly.openssl</groupId>     <artifactId>wildfly-openssl</artifactId>     <version>1.0.9.Final</version> </dependency> ----  Even if WildFly OpenSSL is on the classpath, you can disable its use and revert to the JDK SSL support\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1782743542475}]}
